#

Gourmet Grilled Chicken Burger with Avocado Salsa

$15.99
720 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

EggDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

GrilledGourmetComfort FoodAmerican

Description

A juicy grilled chicken burger topped with fresh avocado salsa and spicy lime aioli, served alongside crispy sweet potato fries for a delightful crunch.

Ingredients

  • Ground Chicken Breast: 1 lb
  • Sweet Potatoes: 2 large
  • Avocado: 1 ripe
  • Red Onion: 1 small
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup
  • Lime Juice: 2 tbsp
  • Mayonnaise: 1/4 cup
  • Chipotle Powder: 1 tsp
  • Garlic Powder: 1 tsp
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Burger Buns: 4 (gluten-free if needed)
